Description:
🇮🇷 #Iranian protestors chase members of #IRGC commanded Imam Ali brigade, of the #Basij paramilitary force.

Additionally, the two other slides show the first set of videos I've seen from #Iran so far showing police officers participating with protesters. Reportedly from #Tehran. Police officers protected anti-regime protesters from #Basij militiamen purportedly. Via Babak Taghvaee on Twitter. Could be indicative this road is a long one for Iran, if there's consistent signs of dissent to levels such as this.

