Description:
RISE WITH THE WOMEN OF IRAN

„Iranian people have been protesting for weeks against the brutal regime of the Islamic Republic. Against the systematic oppression of women and the mandatory headscarf. 
They protest and risk their own lifes. For freedom. 
The regime’s rulers block the internet and prevent journalists from reporting. So they can break up the protest without any notice from worldwide attention. 
But the protests continue. They write songs. They paint pictures. 
They bypass blocks and bans, they post videos and pictures of their protest online. 
They want the worlds attention. So what can we do to make sure that people in Iran are seen? We can at least give our attention!“ Text by Azam Jangravi / @officiallyjoko 

For more information check out this accounts (and the news etc.) Let them know that you see them! Let them know that you care! ❤️

